Script,RosenkranzDbl
window.currentPBSScenario = 'RosenkranzDbl';
window.currentPBSScenarioFilename = 'Rosenkranz_Double';
console.log('PBS: Logging scenario selection for RosenkranzDbl');
fetch('https://bba.harmonicsystems.com/api/scenario/select', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
        'X-Client-Version': '1.0.0'
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        scenario: 'RosenkranzDbl',
        user: whoAmI() || 'anonymous'
    })
}).then(function(r){ console.log('PBS: Server response', r.status); }).catch(function(e){ console.log('PBS: Fetch error', e); });
setDealerCode(`

/*
convention-card-ns: 21GF-GIB
convention-card-ew: 21GF-GIB
auction-filter: (1[CD] +1[HS]|1H +1S)
*/
# Rosenkranz Double
# East opens, South overcalls, West bids
# North responds with Rosenkranz double showing support with a top honor

dealer east

# Predict East's opening suit
es = spades(east)
eh = hearts(east)
ed = diamonds(east)
ec = clubs(east)
eS = es>4 and es>=eh and es>=ed and es>=ec
eH = not eS and eh>4 and eh>=ed and eh>=ec
eD = not (eS or eH) and ((ed>3 and ed>=ec) or ec<3)
eC = not (eS or eH or eD)
eOpens = (eC or eD or eH) and hcp(east)>11 and hcp(east)<15

# South overcalls a major (5+ suit, decent quality, overcall values)
sOC_H = hearts(south)>4 and top5(south,hearts)>1 and hcp(south)>7 and hcp(south)<17
sOC_S = spades(south)>4 and top5(south,spades)>1 and hcp(south)>7 and hcp(south)<17

# South overcalls higher than East's suit
sOvercallH = sOC_H and (eC or eD) and (hearts(south)>spades(south) or spades(south)<5)
sOvercallS = sOC_S and not sOvercallH and (eC or eD or eH)
sOvercalls = sOvercallH or sOvercallS

# West responds
westBids = hcp(west)>5

# North has Rosenkranz double hand:
# 3+ support with A, K, or Q (top3 >= 1) in partner's suit, 6-10 HCP
nSupH = sOvercallH and hearts(north)>2 and top3(north,hearts)>0
nSupS = sOvercallS and spades(north)>2 and top3(north,spades)>0
nRosenkranz = (nSupH or nSupS) and hcp(north)>5 and hcp(north)<11

eOpens and sOvercalls and westBids and nRosenkranz

action printoneline,
average "South HCP   " hcp(south),
average "North HCP   " hcp(north),
average "East HCP    " hcp(east),
average "S overcall H" 100 * sOvercallH,
average "S overcall S" 100 * sOvercallS,
`, "E", true)
Script
Button,Rosenkranz Dbl,\n\
--- Rosenkranz Double\n\
After LHO opens，partner overcalls，and RHO bids:\n\
. Double = 3+ support with A，K，or Q in partner's suit，6-10 HCP\n\
. Simple raise = 3+ support WITHOUT a top honor，6-10 HCP\n\
. Cuebid = 10+ HCP with support (too strong for Rosenkranz)\n\
If RHO doubles instead of bidding，Redouble = Rosenkranz.\n\
Applies through the 2-level only.\n\
NOTE: BBA does not play Rosenkranz doubles.\n\
https://www.bridgebum.com/rosenkranz_double.php\n\
%RosenkranzDbl%,backgroundColor=lightpink
